<p>究竟very good 好d 定係quite perfect 好d 呢?</p>
<p>今日先知道完全quite perfect 係contradictroy ge...quite 就係唔完整ge, perfect 就咁完美...orz</p>
<p>但堂講到係brian 講出口ge 時侯, 就變左無問題lol</p>
<p>一個好的powerpoint presentation要:</p>
<ol>
<li>一個slide d point 唔好多過十個</li>
<li>一個point 唔好多過十個字</li>
<li>字同背景的對比要大(黑白)</li>
<li>個背景的顏色轉變唔好太大</li>
<li>animation 唔好太多太慢, 但適當的animation 可以catah attention</li>
<li>give handout if u have a lot of infomation at the end to remind audiences</li>
<li>要組織好powerpoint eg. opening &gt; part1 &gt; ending</li>
<li>要適合對象</li>
<li>catch audiences' attention by stating a story/joke in the beginning</li>
<li>give procedure to audience</li>
<li>係最後．．．要有summary</li>
<li>guide d 人moving from 一個point 去另一個point</li>
<li>比具體例子/比喻...eg. mimi d 課好悶...好似坐係一間無聲音ge 房咁</li>
<li>do NOT read from the powerpoint&gt;&gt;&gt;use own word and more eliboration</li>
<li>don't focus on mistakes</li>
</ol>